VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'respectable two CPUs and 8 GB of RAM. And right now, you can save a ton of money with their Black Friday deal and then save even more money after that by stacking it with the Fire Ship discount code. In this demo, we\'ll build both client and server apps. So, I\'m choosing'

[02:43] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
