AUDIO: 'Hostinger. But now that we have a server lined up, let\'s take a look at the code. Here I have a dead simple Node.js JS app using hono to build a restful API. When someone navigates to this protected route, it will give them some highly'

[03:08] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
